and being propelled^f36 by the other {motile} air, it shows intimation and it flexes and extends and it wriggles the hands and feet, doing so in the postures comprising of walking, standing, sitting and lying down. 
So this mechanism of elements carries on like a magic trick, deceiving foolish people with the male and female sex and so on.
This is how they should be given attention by particles.
^n350^en93k^i[4. As to characteristic, etc].: he should advert to the four elements in this way: “The earth element—what are its characteristic, function, manifestation?” {defining them in this way}: The earth element has the characteristic of hardness. Its function is to act as a foundation. It is manifested as receiving. 
