^n713^en69t 4. That ^z6[arising from temperature] becomes evident through cool and heat. 
For materiality that is originated when it is hot is parched, stale and ugly. ^pts624 
Materiality originated by cool temperature is plump, fresh, tender, smooth, and soft to touch.	
Discerning that, ^paste "The materiality occurring when it is hot ceases there without reaching the time when it is cool. 
